Help me! Oh, God.

871
01:16:44,170 --> 01:16:46,090
Help me!

872
01:16:47,210 --> 01:16:49,129
Help me!

873
01:16:51,329 --> 01:16:53,929
Help me!

874
01:16:58,169 --> 01:17:02,049
<i>I saw him.
