896
01:18:25,284 --> 01:18:27,324
Stop it, Henry!

897
01:18:27,324 --> 01:18:29,603
Stop!

898
01:18:29,603 --> 01:18:30,803
No!

899
01:18:30,803 --> 01:18:32,323
DR. ALLEN: Henry.

900
